&lt;li&gt;Strong critical thinking and analytical skills; able to assess situations beyond standard procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have professional proficiency in English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High attention to detail, especially when handling confidential HR data.&lt;/li&

